  "description": "A serene coastal scene depicting a rocky shoreline meeting the ocean under a clear blue sky. The foreground is comprised of a sandy beach scattered with numerous dark grey and brown rocks.  Several larger, seaweed-covered rock formations rise from the shallow turquoise water near the shore, extending further out towards the deeper blue ocean. Gentle waves are breaking against the rocks and the beach. The overall impression is one of natural beauty and tranquility.",
